  "slug": "rocky-road-slice",
  "title": "Rocky road slice",
  "subtitle": "Chocolate, marshmallow, and biscuit",
  "excerpt": "A traybake of dark chocolate, butter, golden syrup, broken biscuits, miniature marshmallows, and raisins. No oven required. Set in the fridge and sliced into rectangles.",
  "type": "RECIPE",
  "sourceNotes": "Rocky road is an American confection of the 1920s, originally an ice cream flavour. The British traybake version (fridge-set rather than baked) entered domestic cookery in the mid-twentieth century. This version follows the standard British domestic formula.",
  "body": {
    "type": "doc",
    "content": [
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Rocky road needs no oven and almost no skill, but the ratio of chocolate to filler still matters. Too much biscuit and the slice crumbles and tastes floury; too little and it is pure confectionery. This recipe keeps the biscuit and marshmallow at 60% of the total weight, leaving the chocolate as the structure and flavour.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "ingredientsList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "ingredientsGroup",
            "attrs": {
              "title": null
            },
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "ingredient",
                "attrs": {
                  "slug": "dark-chocolate",
                  "unit": "g",
                  "prepNote": "70% cocoa, broken into pieces",
                  "quantity": 300,
                  "isOptional": false
                }
              },
              {
                "type": "ingredient",
                "attrs": {
                  "slug": "unsalted-butter",
                  "unit": "g",
                  "prepNote": null,
                  "quantity": 100,
                  "isOptional": false
                }
              },
              {
                "type": "ingredient",
                "attrs": {
                  "slug": "golden-syrup",
                  "unit": "tbsp",
                  "prepNote": null,
                  "quantity": 2,
                  "isOptional": false
                }
              },
              {
                "type": "ingredient",
                "attrs": {
                  "slug": "digestive-biscuits",
